OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FWatch the latest report from ITV News
OL,7,FWest Country as the drinking water
OL,8,Fscandal continues in South Devon.
OL,10,FSouth West Water has given an estimate
OL,11,Fon when the boil water notice will be
OL,12,Flifted from all households in , South
OL,13,FDevon.
OL,15,FIt follows an outbreak of a diarrhoea
OL,16,Fand vomiting illness,
OL,18,FThe UK Health Security Agency has so
OL,19,Ffar confirmed 46 cases of the parasite
OL,20,F- but more than 100 other people have
OL,21,Freported similar symptoms.
