OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FAround 17,000 households were told to
OL,7,Fboil any water they consumed from
OL,8,FWednesday 15 May onwards.
OL,10,FOn Saturday 18 May, that notice was
OL,11,Flifted from the Alston network area -
OL,12,Faround 14,000 homes - but remains in
OL,13,Fplace for 2,500 households in the
OL,14,FHillhead, upper Brixham and Kingswear
OL,15,Fareas.
