OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FSouth West Water has promised an extra
OL,7,F#100 compensation to customers who are
OL,8,Fstill under a boil water notice in
OL,9,FBrixham.
OL,11,FAll of those affected were initially
OL,12,Ftold they would get #15, but this rose
OL,13,Fto #100 shortly afterwards.
OL,15,FNow, anyone living in Hillhead, upper
OL,16,FBrixham and Kingswear, is entitled to
OL,17,F#215 total compensation.
OL,19,FSouth West Water said that equated to
OL,20,Fnearly half the average annual water
OL,21,Fbill.
