OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FWhere did the parasite come from?
OL,8,FSouth West Water said in a statement
OL,9,Fon Sunday 19 May: "We have already
OL,10,Fidentified a probable cause at
OL,11,FHillhead - a damaged air valve on
OL,12,Fprivate farmland - and are urgently
OL,13,Finvestigating how this happened."
OL,15,FEarlier this week, it was suggested
OL,16,Fthat the parasite itself could have
OL,17,Fcome from cow manure on the farmland.
