OL,3,CUpdate on when boil water notice could
OL,4,Cbe fully lifted in Brixham
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News West
OL,7,FCountry on Sunday 19 May, incident
OL,8,Fdirector David Harris gave an
OL,9,Findication of when the boil notice
OL,10,Fcould be lifted from all areas.
OL,12,FHe said: "We will lift the boil water
OL,13,Fnotice in the Hillhead area as soon as
OL,14,Fwe can in agreement with our public
OL,15,Fhealth partners.
OL,17,F"We have to flush our network of
OL,18,Fcryptosporidium and then get a series
OL,19,Fof clear test results.
